original: Kilander, Erik Tage Eugen, länsassessor, Växjö, f. 34/7/02 d Ulkne, Skarab. 1., av löjtn. Claes K. o. Maria Jonsson, G. 43 m. Märta Carlsson. Barn: Claes-Olof f. 44, Anders 45. — Stud:ex. 21, jur. kand. 26. Tingstjg. i Askims m. fl. hds doms. 26-28, ans t. v. länsstyr. i Gbgs o. Boh. län 28-44, länsassessor i Växjö sed. 45. Bitr. sekr. i kommunindeln :-komm. 43-45.
translated: Kilander, Erik Tage Eugen, county assessor, Växjö, b. July 2nd, 1902, d. Ulkne, Skaraborg County. Son of Lieutenant Claes K. and Maria Jonsson. Married in 1943 to Märta Carlsson. Children: Claes-Olof b. 1944, Anders b. 1945. Completed studentexamen (high school diploma) in 1921, law degree in 1926. Served as legal clerk in various district courts, including Askims, from 1926-1928. Employed at the County Administration Board in Gothenburg and Bohuslän County from 1928-1944. Appointed county assessor in Växjö in 1945. Deputy secretary in the Municipal Division Committee from 1943-1945.
